Grindrod Says Profit Declined 36% to $39 Million in Six Months to June 30

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-08-18T06:05:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-18/grindrod-says-profit-declined-36-to-39-million-in-six-months-to-june-30.html
Grindrod Ltd. (GND)  said first-half net
income declined to 277.4 million rand compared with 435.5
million rand a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
